b"[![](../../cdshop/cdinfo.jpg)](../../cdshop/index.htm)  \n[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)\n[Previous](sbe48498.htm)  [Next](sbe48500.htm)\n\n* * *\n\n2\\. And on account of an inferential mark.\n\nInferential mark here means Sm _ri_ ti. Sm _ri_ ti also declares that that\nknowledge which effects Release is of the nature of continued representation.\nMeditation therefore has to be repeated.--Here terminates the adhikara _n_ a\nof 'repetition.'\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: 3. But as the Self...](sbe48500.htm)\n\n"